      <scopecontent id="aspace_ecc0b0d88caea69ec3d17dc831eb19fc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of videorecordings of the Gibbs Symposium held at Yale in 1989. The symposium was held in honor of Josiah Willard Gibbs, a leader in theoretical physics.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
